---
// ContentParagraphs.astro — Contributions (Final Fixed Version)
---

<section id="content-paragraphs" class="content-section">
  <div class="section-container">

    <h2 class="section-heading reveal">Key Contributions</h2>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <p class="intro-text reveal">
      We evaluate SenseGuard in Connected and Autonomous Vehicles (CAVs)—a demanding setting with massive sensor data, strict real-time constraints, and safety-critical decisions. Solutions that succeed here generalize naturally to broader robotic systems.
    </p>

    <!-- Cards -->
    <div class="contribution-grid reveal">

      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="contribution-card">
        <img 
          src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1cCOkD-07gkVU_4yxMg31fcoXqf5gX9MT&sz=w1000" 
          alt="Adaptive filtering visualization"
          class="card-img"
        />
        <h3>Adaptive Sensory Filtering</h3>
        <p>
          A vibration- and context-aware policy dynamically removes redundant data while preserving critical information.
          Leveraging lightweight semantics and reinforcement learning, it maintains real-time efficiency under tight compute budgets.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="contribution-card">
        <img 
          src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=16Yvv_30e39Ls8XdcL4X_U8xKTXmARlnF&sz=w1000" 
          alt="Failure aligned data curation"
          class="card-img"
        />
        <h3>Failure-Aligned Data Curation</h3>
        <p>
          Instead of logging everything, the system captures compact, high-value data when perception degrades—focusing on critical events that accelerate model improvement.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="contribution-card">
        <img 
          src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1cCOkD-07gkVU_4yxMg31fcoXqf5gX9MT&sz=w1000" 
          alt="Performance results"
          class="card-img"
        />
        <h3>Strong Real-World Performance</h3>
        <p>
          Achieves up to <strong>+20% accuracy</strong>, <strong>75% lower trajectory error</strong>, reduced latency,
          and <strong>32% storage savings</strong> across benchmarks and real-world deployments.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>

/* ===== SECTION ===== */
.content-section {
  padding: 4rem 2rem 3rem;
}

/* ===== HEADING ===== */
.section-heading {
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  color: #223253;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  position: relative;
}

.section-heading::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -6px;
  left: 0;
  width: 55px;
  height: 3px;
  background: #c05e3c;
}

/* ===== INTRO FIX ===== */
.intro-text {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 100%;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: #444;
  margin-bottom: 2.2rem;

  text-align: justify;
  text-justify: inter-word;
}

/* ===== GRID ===== */
.contribution-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.6rem;
}

/* ===== CARD ===== */
.contribution-card {
  padding: 1.2rem;
  border-radius: 12px;

  background: #ffffff;
  border: 1px solid #e4e8ef;

  transition: all 0.25s ease;
}

/* ===== IMAGE ===== */
.card-img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 150px;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;

  background: #f2f2f2;
}

/* ===== HOVER ===== */
.contribution-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  border-color: #c05e3c;
}

/* ===== TITLE ===== */
.contribution-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #223253;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

/* ===== TEXT ===== */
.contribution-card p {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #555;

  text-align: justify;
}

/* ===== MOBILE ===== */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .intro-text {
    text-align: left;
  }
}

</style>